      "updated_at": "2016-05-12 13:45:39 UTC",
      "body": "The above is consistent with other formatting options that align all parameters on the column after `(`. For styles that do not use this formatting, a more consistent variant is:\r\n```scala\r\nwhile (!hasReachedEof(curr) &&\r\n    !statementStarts.contains(hash(tokens(curr.splits.length).left))) {\r\n```\r\nwith 4 spaces (like `if` too)"
    },
